TT smiles and laughed loudly.

TT:  AND I WANTED TO LEAVE HAHAHAHAHA!  PREHISTORIC EARTH IS RIGHT 
WHERE HE'LL HEAD!  AND WHEN HE GETS HERE I'LL BE WAITING!  NOW LETS 
GO!  BEAST MODE!

He turns in to a Rhino and follows Panthos laughing all the way.

OOC: Please don't make me give the full history in one day.  Let me 
keep some secrets.  Just trust me on this one.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Jonathan" <jhogan@r...> wrote:
> TT:  I am no longer a Maximal.  My shame is to great.  This ensignia 
> is only a symbol of what I was, and what I hope to be again someday. 
 
> It is all I have for Iam now nothing.  But I suppose I could be a 
> Maximal if it could get me off the planet.  Where are we again?
> 
> {Panthos}
> 
>     "The name is Panthos by the way. As for where we are my star 
charts listed it as earth, though I don't see anything even remotely 
human running around so I couldn't even guess the time frame."
> 
>     Turning the panther moved back toward the jungle his designation 
switching back to predacon internally. "Come on it's back this way."
